        <item>
          <title>Trump turns to critic of COVID mandates to run NIH</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Dr. Jay Bhattacharya, a Stanford health researcher, is in line to lead the National Institutes of Health. Early in the pandemic he argued against lockdowns and focusing on people at highest risk.]]></description>
